# HTB Walkthroughs Ignore File

# Protect VPN and connection files
*.ovpn
*.conf
**/vpn/

# Protect Loot and Credentials
**/loot/
**/*.hash
**/*.ntlm
**/*.kdbx

# Python/System artifacts
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.env
.venv/
env/
venv/
.DS_Store

# Scans can sometimes be huge or contain session data
**/scans/*.xml
**/scans/*.nmap
